<Style id="remote"><IconStyle><color>ffb5638e</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/wht-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.72</scale></LabelStyle></Style>
<Style id="caution"><IconStyle><color>ff4f53d9</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/paddle/wht-circle.png</href></Icon></IconStyle><LabelStyle><scale>0.72</scale></LabelStyle></Style>
<Folder><name>曼谷 Bangkok Food</name>
<Placemark><name>1. Rongros 河景泰餐 Rongros</name><description><![CDATA[河景晚餐 / 泰餐 | core | 老城 / Wat Arun view<br/>适合寺庙日收尾，主打 Wat Arun 河景和情侣晚餐氛围。<br/>Notes: 热门河景位建议提前订位; 作为 date night 比夜市更稳。<br/>Google Maps: Rongros Bangkok Wat Arun view restaurant<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.4917,13.7469,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>2. The Deck 河景餐厅 The Deck by Arun Residence</name><description><![CDATA[河景晚餐 / 泰餐 | optional | 老城 / Wat Arun view<br/>经典郑王庙对岸视角餐厅，可作为 Rongros 替代。<br/>Notes: 订位时确认河景位。<br/>Google Maps: The Deck by Arun Residence Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.4912,13.7444,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>3. Thong Smith 船面 Thong Smith</name><description><![CDATA[泰式船面 / 商场餐厅 | core | Siam / CentralWorld / ICONSIAM 多分店<br/>小红书高频推荐，适合商场日就近吃。<br/>Notes: 不用专门绕路，选最近分店即可。<br/>Google Maps: Thong Smith CentralWorld Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5392,13.7465,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>4. Karun 泰奶 Karun Thai Tea</name><description><![CDATA[泰奶 / 甜品 | core | Siam / CentralWorld / ICONSIAM 多分店<br/>适合和 Thong Smith、CentralWorld、ICONSIAM 同步安排。<br/>Notes: 当作商场日补给，不单独跑一趟。<br/>Google Maps: Karun Thai Tea CentralWorld Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5392,13.7465,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>5. Factory Coffee Factory Coffee Bangkok</name><description><![CDATA[咖啡 | optional | Phaya Thai / Ratchathewi<br/>网红咖啡点，适合在 Siam / Phaya Thai 附近顺路。<br/>Notes: 可能排队; 不建议为了咖啡破坏路线节奏。<br/>Google Maps: Factory Coffee Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5328,13.7564,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>6. Mae Varee 芒果糯米饭 Mae Varee Mango Sticky Rice</name><description><![CDATA[芒果糯米饭 / 甜品 | optional | Thonglor<br/>经典芒果糯米饭，适合去 Thonglor / Sukhumvit 时顺路。<br/>Notes: 离主行程较远，不要专门绕路。<br/>Google Maps: Mae Varee Mango Sticky Rice Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5784,13.7246,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>7. Phed Mark 打抛饭 Phed Mark</name><description><![CDATA[打抛饭 / 快餐 | optional | Ekkamai<br/>适合喜欢重口和辣味时去。<br/>Notes: 位置偏东，不住 Sukhumvit 则不建议专门绕太远。<br/>Google Maps: Phed Mark Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5855,13.7193,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>8. Jeh O Chula 妈妈面 Jeh O Chula</name><description><![CDATA[夜宵 / Mama 面 | core | Banthat Thong / Chula<br/>朱拉美食区高频网红店，适合作为 Siam + Chula 晚餐候选。<br/>Notes: 热门时段排队长; 把它当候选而不是硬目标。<br/>Google Maps: Jeh O Chula Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5237,13.74,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>9. Go-Ang 水门鸡饭 Go-Ang Pratunam Chicken Rice</name><description><![CDATA[海南鸡饭 / 快餐 | optional | Pratunam / CentralWorld<br/>CentralWorld / Big C 附近可顺路尝试的经典鸡饭。<br/>Notes: 不用为了它排太久; 附近选择很多。<br/>Google Maps: Go-Ang Pratunam Chicken Rice Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5405,13.7501,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>10. PangCha 泰茶甜品 PangCha</name><description><![CDATA[甜品 / 泰茶 | optional | Siam / CentralWorld 多分店<br/>甜品/泰茶候选，适合商场日休息。<br/>Notes: 如果已经喝 Karun，可不必重复。<br/>Google Maps: PangCha Siam Paragon Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5347,13.7468,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>11. On Lok Yun 老咖啡早餐 On Lok Yun</name><description><![CDATA[早餐 / 老咖啡店 | optional | 老城 / Wang Burapha<br/>老城复古早餐点，可作为寺庙日早午餐备选。<br/>Notes: 更偏本地老店体验，不适合追求精致环境。<br/>Google Maps: On Lok Yun Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.4996,13.7469,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>12. 唐人街街头小吃带 Yaowarat street food zone</name><description><![CDATA[街头小吃 / 夜市 | core | 唐人街<br/>沿 Yaowarat 分摊尝试比锁死单店更适合情侣。<br/>Notes: 准备现金; 人多且热，注意随身物品。<br/>Google Maps: Yaowarat Road street food Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.51,13.7394,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>13. Banthat Thong 美食街 Banthat Thong food street</name><description><![CDATA[美食街 / 夜宵 | core | Chula / Siam<br/>Siam 商圈晚餐/夜宵更灵活的区域选择。<br/>Notes: 可以把 Jeh O Chula 当候选，不必死排。<br/>Google Maps: Banthat Thong Road food Bangkok<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>100.5253,13.7405,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder><name>普吉岛 Phuket Food</name>
<Placemark><name>1. One Chun 普吉本地菜 One Chun Cafe & Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[普吉本地菜 / Bib Gourmand | core | Phuket Old Town<br/>普吉老街核心本地菜候选，适合和老街同一天。<br/>Notes: 热门时段可能排队; 可和 Raya / Tu Kab Khao 替换。<br/>Google Maps: One Chun Cafe Restaurant Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3894,7.8848,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>2. Raya 老宅本地菜 Raya Restaurant Phuket</name><description><![CDATA[普吉本地菜 / 老宅 | optional | Phuket Old Town<br/>经典老宅普吉菜，适合更正式本地菜体验。<br/>Notes: 通常比街头小吃高。<br/>Google Maps: Raya Restaurant Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.391,7.8848,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>3. Tu Kab Khao 普吉菜 Tu Kab Khao</name><description><![CDATA[普吉本地菜 | core | Phuket Old Town<br/>老街区域方便的普吉菜选择，环境适合情侣。<br/>Notes: 可作为 One Chun 替代。<br/>Google Maps: Tu Kab Khao Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.389,7.885,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>4. Mee Ton Poe 福建面 Mee Ton Poe</name><description><![CDATA[福建面 / 快餐 | optional | Phuket Old Town<br/>普吉老街小吃候选，适合轻量午餐。<br/>Notes: 不要和重餐叠太多。<br/>Google Maps: Mee Ton Poe Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3927,7.8821,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>5. Torry's Ice Cream Torry's Ice Cream</name><description><![CDATA[甜品 / 冰淇淋 | core | Soi Romanee<br/>Soi Romanee 拍照和休息顺路甜品。<br/>Notes: 适合老街下午休息。<br/>Google Maps: Torry's Ice Cream Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3897,7.8848,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>6. Dibuk Restaurant Dibuk Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[老街餐厅 / Thai-French | optional | Phuket Old Town<br/>想要比夜市更安静的老街晚餐时可考虑。<br/>Notes: 需要看当天订位和营业。<br/>Google Maps: Dibuk Restaurant Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3879,7.8858,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>7. Rawai 海鲜市场 Rawai Seafood Market</name><description><![CDATA[海鲜 / 晚餐 | core | Rawai<br/>南部海岸线 + 神仙半岛之后的晚餐核心。<br/>Notes: 先问每公斤价、加工费和总价。<br/>Google Maps: Rawai Seafood Market Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: exact-ish]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.329,7.775,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>8. Mor Mu Dong 本地海鲜 Mor Mu Dong</name><description><![CDATA[本地海鲜 / 泰餐 | optional | Chalong / mangrove area<br/>偏本地感的海鲜/泰餐候选，适合包车路线顺路。<br/>Notes: 位置不如老街/Rawai 方便，适合包车时考虑。<br/>Google Maps: Mor Mu Dong Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3618,7.8503,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>9. Kan Eang @ Pier Kan Eang @ Pier</name><description><![CDATA[海鲜 / 海边餐厅 | optional | Chalong Pier<br/>查龙码头附近海鲜餐厅，适合查龙寺/南部路线。<br/>Notes: 比市场式海鲜更餐厅化。<br/>Google Maps: Kan Eang at Pier Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3426,7.8196,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>10. Three Monkeys 森林餐厅 Three Monkeys Restaurant</name><description><![CDATA[景观餐厅 / 泰餐 | optional | Phuket Town hillside<br/>适合想要环境和照片的景观餐厅。<br/>Notes: 更偏体验和环境，不一定是性价比最高。<br/>Google Maps: Three Monkeys Restaurant Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3508,7.892,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>11. Tunk Ka Cafe 山顶餐厅 Tunk Ka Cafe</name><description><![CDATA[观景餐厅 / 泰餐 | optional | Khao Rang<br/>普吉镇附近观景晚餐候选。<br/>Notes: 天气差时视野会下降。<br/>Google Maps: Tunk Ka Cafe Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.378,7.8945,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>12. Lard Yai 夜市小吃 Lard Yai Sunday Walking Street food</name><description><![CDATA[夜市 / 小吃 | core | Phuket Old Town<br/>如果 8/16 在普吉，正好可以安排周日夜市。<br/>Notes: 人多但气氛好，适合分摊吃。<br/>Google Maps: Lard Yai Sunday Walking Street Phuket<br/>Coordinate confidence: exact-ish]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.388,7.8845,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>13. Central Phuket 雨天吃饭 Central Phuket dining</name><description><![CDATA[商场 / 雨天餐饮 | optional | Central Phuket<br/>雨天、补给、简单吃饭的室内备选。<br/>Notes: 不需要专门安排很久。<br/>Google Maps: Central Phuket restaurants<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.3682,7.8915,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder><name>瑶亚岛 Koh Yao Yai Food</name>
<Placemark><name>1. Santhiya 酒店内餐厅 Santhiya in-resort dining</name><description><![CDATA[酒店餐厅 / 度假晚餐 | core | Santhiya / Loh Pared Bay<br/>四晚的安全主轴：早餐、泳池日、七夕晚餐和不想外出时的晚餐。<br/>Notes: 入住时确认开放餐厅、海景位和七夕私密晚餐。<br/>Google Maps: Santhiya Koh Yao Yai Resort restaurants<br/>Coordinate confidence: exact-ish]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.579,7.983,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>2. Loh Pared 海滩小店区 Loh Pared Beach local restaurants</name><description><![CDATA[海滩小店 / 本地泰餐 | core | Loh Pared Beach<br/>Santhiya 周边最近的外出吃饭方向，适合不想每天吃酒店餐时使用。<br/>Notes: 小岛营业时间会变，出门前问酒店或用 Google Maps 确认。<br/>Google Maps: Loh Pared Beach restaurants Koh Yao Yai<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.5785,7.9808,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>3. Gypsy / 海滩酒吧方向 Gypsy beach bar direction</name><description><![CDATA[海滩酒吧 / 轻食 | optional | Loh Pared Beach<br/>Loh Pared Beach 一带的轻松海滩氛围方向，适合散步时临时选择。<br/>Notes: 瑶亚岛整体更安静，夜生活不要期待太高。<br/>Google Maps: Gypsy Bar Koh Yao Yai Loh Pared Beach<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.575,7.98,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>4. Prunai 本地午餐方向 Prunai local lunch area</name><description><![CDATA[本地餐 / 包车午餐 | core | Prunai / local village<br/>岛内轻量环线时可以让司机推荐的本地餐方向。<br/>Notes: 问酒店/司机通常比硬找网红店更靠谱。<br/>Google Maps: Prunai Koh Yao Yai restaurants<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#core</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.584,7.946,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>5. Laem Haad 北部小吃 / 饮品方向 Laem Haad north route snacks</name><description><![CDATA[沙洲路线补给 | optional | Laem Haad / north Koh Yao Yai<br/>去 Laem Haad 沙洲时作为饮品/小吃补给方向。<br/>Notes: 核心是潮汐和拍照，不是专门为了吃。<br/>Google Maps: Laem Haad Koh Yao Yai restaurants<br/>Coordinate confidence: area]]></description><styleUrl>#optional</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.607,8.106,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
<Placemark><name>6. 私人船野餐 / 船餐 Private boat picnic / boat lunch</name><description><![CDATA[私人船 / 出海餐 | remote | Hong Islands / Phang Nga direction<br/>如果包私人船，提前确认是否包含饮水、水果、午餐或野餐。<br/>Notes: 必须看海况; 不要安排在离岛前一天。<br/>Google Maps: Hong Islands private boat lunch Koh Yao Yai<br/>Coordinate confidence: direction]]></description><styleUrl>#remote</styleUrl><Point><coordinates>98.6741,8.2203,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark>
</Folder>
</Document></kml>